Hello, and welcome to my first "big" project with AROWMAX ! 
This map is a map for the bhopper AROWMAX. He test, and gave my ideas. So, thanks to him ! 
There is music, but he can stop.
There is 9 stage, one KZ, pretty hard, but there is a noob part. (pretty long)
Some tips : In the cave part : duck and jump bhop or you wi'll knock you head in the light.
Please, gave you rate, it's important !
Good luck, and have fun !
